"""
    Test generator feature.
    """
def generator():
    """
        A generator for testing.
        """
    for i in range(4):
        yield [(j + i) for j in range(5)]
itemsets, _ = itemsets_from_transactions(generator, min_support=3 / 4)
assert itemsets[3] == {(2, 3, 4): 3, (3, 4, 5): 3}
